Recipe
// Recipe for the xth fibonacci number

Ingredients
set chocolate
set banana
set sugar
set milk

Utensils
whisk with x
    1. check x is 1
        1. serve 1
        2. end
    2. check x is 2
        1. serve 3
        2. end
    3. set chocolate to 1
    4. set banana to 3
    5. set sugar to x minus 1
    6. while sugar above 1
        1. set milk to 3 multiply banana minus chocolate
        2. set chocolate to banana
        3. set banana to milk
        4. set sugar to sugar minus 1
        5. end
    7. serve milk
    8. end

Steps
    1. taste whisk with 8  // expect: 987
    2. end
